# ‚ö†Ô∏è CRITICAL RULES - DO NOT VIOLATE!
# =====================================================

## 1. File Size Limit
MAXIMUM: 300 lines per file
If > 300 lines: Split into logical parts

## 2. Import Rules
```dart
// ‚úÖ CORRECT - Use barrel exports
import 'package:example_app/core/theme/index.dart';
import 'package:example_app/core/widgets/index.dart';

// ‚ùå WRONG - Direct file imports from src
import 'package:example_app/core/theme/tokens/app_colors.dart';
```

## 3. Hardcoded Colors FORBIDDEN
```dart
// ‚ùå WRONG
color: Color(0xFF5B7CFF)
color: Colors.red

// ‚úÖ CORRECT
color: AppColors.primary
color: Theme.of(context).colorScheme.primary
```

## 4. Hardcoded Spacing FORBIDDEN
```dart
// ‚ùå WRONG
padding: EdgeInsets.all(16)
SizedBox(height: 8)

// ‚úÖ CORRECT
padding: EdgeInsets.all(AppSpacing.lg)
SizedBox(height: AppSpacing.sm)
```

## 5. Touch Target Minimum 48dp
```dart
// ‚ùå WRONG
SizedBox(width: 32, height: 32)

// ‚úÖ CORRECT
SizedBox(width: 48, height: 48)
```

# =====================================================
# üß© COMPONENT SPECIFICATIONS
# =====================================================

## AppButton
Variants: primary, secondary, outline, text, destructive
Sizes: small (36h), medium (44h), large (52h)
Features: loading state, icons, isExpanded, disabled (50% opacity)

## AppIconButton
Variants: filled, tonal, outline, ghost
Sizes: small (40), medium (44), large (52)
Features: tooltip (required!), badge, selected state

## AppTextField
Features: label, hint, error, prefix icon, suffix widget, validation

## AppModal (Responsive)
Phone (< 600px): Bottom sheet, drag handle, rounded top 20dp
Tablet (‚â• 600px): Center dialog, max-width 560px, rounded 16dp

## AppToast
Types: success (#4ADE80), error (#EF4444), warning (#FACC15), info (#5B7CFF)
Features: auto-dismiss 4s, swipe to dismiss, action button

